Map's textures based on the surf_rebel_resistance. This jail includes basic cells, weaponary, shoot 4 shoot arena, football pitch, swimming pool and little bhop area.

Credits:
I used the unlimited ammo prefab made by:
DOLG.XxX(PiSt)
link: [LINK](http://www.gamebanana.com/css/prefabs/5717 "Unlimited ammo prefab")

If you like the map please rate it and if you want you can leave a comment with improvements. Also say if you notice any bugs.

The map file is in a zip file, unpack it and put the file in your cstrike/maps folder.
